data.description: Location, location, location. This conveniently located home in the heart of Florence has 3 bedroom, 2 baths, and has recently been remodeled. Newer flooring, paint, stainless steel kitchen appliances, granite countertops, and updated bathrooms. The unfinished basement with walkout will allow for plenty of additional room for storage or even a gaming area. A great way to start your New Year off right, schedule to see it now!
